Efficacy and cost-effectiveness of early antiretroviral therapy and partners' 
pre-exposure prophylaxis among men who have sex with men in Shenyang, China: a 
prospective cohort and costing study.

Hu QH(1)(2)(3)(4), Meyers K(5), Xu JJ(1)(2)(3)(4), Chu ZX(1)(2)(3)(4), Zhang 
J(1)(2)(3)(4), Ding HB(1)(2)(3)(4), Han XX(1)(2)(3)(4), Jiang YJ(1)(2)(3)(4), 
