The Changing Clinical Spectrum of Hypophysitis.

Chiloiro S(1), Capoluongo ED(2), Tartaglione T(3), Giampietro A(1), Bianchi 
A(1), Giustina A(4), Pontecorvi A(1), De Marinis L(5).

Author information:
(1)Pituitary Unit, Department of Endocrinology, Fondazione A Gemelli, IRCCS, 
Università Cattolica del Sacro Cuore, Rome, Italy.
(2)Department of Molecular Medicine, Università Federico II, Naple, Italy.
(3)Department of Radiology, Istituto Dermopatico dell'Immacolata, Rome and 
